ke]]\n* [[PILOT]]\n* [[Hartmann pipeline|Pipelines]]\n* [[Pizza (programming language)|Pizza]]\n* [[PL-11]]\n* [[PL/0]]\n* [[Programming Language for Business|PL/B]]\n* [[PL/C]]\n* [[PL/I]] \u2013 ISO 6160\n* [[PL/M]]\n* [[PL/P]]\n* [[PL/SQL]]\n* [[PL360]]\n* [[PLANC]]\n* [[Plankalk\u00fcl]]\n* [[Planner (programming language)|Planner]]\n* [[PLEX (programming language)|PLEX]]\n* [[PLEXIL]]\n* [[Plus (programming language)|Plus]]\n* [[POP-11]]\n* [[POP-2]]\n<!-- [[Poplog]] is an IDE -->\n* [[PostScript]]\n* [[Amiga E#PortablE|PortablE]]\n* [[POV-Ray|POV-Ray SDL]]\n* [[Powerhouse (programming language)|Powerhouse]]\n* [[PowerBuilder]] \u2013 4GL GUI application generator from Sybase\n* [[PowerShell]]\n* [[Polymorphic Programming Language|PPL]]\n* [[Processing (programming language)|Processing]]\n* [[Processing.js]]\n* [[Prograph]]\n* [[PROIV]]\n* [[Prolog]]\n* [[PROMAL]]\n* [[Promela]]\n* [[PROSE modeling language]]\n* [[Protel|PROTEL]]\n* [[ProvideX]]\n* [[Pro*C]]\n* [[Pure (programming language)|Pure]]\n* [[Pure Data]]\n<!-- PureBasic is on BASIC dialects - see [[List of BASIC dialects]] page -->\n* [[PureScript]]\n* [[Python (programming language)|Python]]\n}}\n\n== Q ==\n{{columns-list|colwidth=22em|\n* [[Q (programming language from Kx Systems)]]\n* [[Q Sharp|Q# (Microsoft programming language)]]\n* [[Qalb (programming language)|Qalb]]\n<!-- [[QBasic]] - see [[List of BASIC dialects]] page -->\n* [[QtScript]]\n* [[QuakeC]]\n* [[Quantum programming|QPL]]\n* [[Qbasic]]\n* [[.QL]]\n}}\n\n== R ==\n{{columns-list|colwidth=22em|\n* [[R (programming language)|R]]\n* [[R++]]\n* [[Racket (programming language)|Racket]]\n* [[Raku (programming language)|Raku]]\n* [[RAPID]]\n* [[Rapira]]\n* [[Ratfiv]]\n* [[Ratfor]]\n<!-- [[RBScript]] \u2013 see [[List of BASIC dialects]] -->\n<!--Do not add RBX.Lua onto the list. Roblox Lua is just a slightly modified version of Lua with added and removed functions.-->\n* [[rc]]\n* [[React (web framework)|React]]\n* [[React Native]]\n* [[Rea