a (programming language)|Zebra, ZPL, ZPL2]]\n* [[Zeno (programming language)|Zeno]]\n* [[ZetaLisp]]\n* [[ZOPL]]\n* [[Z shell|Zsh]]\n* [[ZPL (programming language)|ZPL]]\n* [[Z++]]\n}}\n\n== See also ==\n{{Sister project links|Programming languages|wikt=programming language|b=Computer Programming|s=How to Think Like a Computer Scientist|commons=Category:Programming languages}}\n* [[Lists of programming languages]]\n* [[List of programming languages by type]]\n* [[Comparison of programming languages]]\n* [[List of BASIC dialects by platform]]\n* [[List of markup languages]]\n* [[List of stylesheet languages]]\n* [[History of programming languages]]\n* [[:Category:Programming languages]]\n* {{Wikibooks-inline|List of hello world programs}}\n{{Portal|Computer programming|left=yes}}\n\n{{Programming languages}}\n\n[[Category:Lists of programming languages| ]]\n[[Category:Computer programming|*]]\n", "name_user": "2409:4072:109:2313::255:a0b1", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_programming_languages"}
